              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-600/20 text-yellow-400 rounded-full text-sm">PHP</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-600/20 text-green-400 rounded-full text-sm">MySQL</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-600/20 text-purple-400 rounded-full text-sm">JavaScript</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-600/20 text-red-400 rounded-full text-sm">CSS3</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-600/20 text-orange-400 rounded-full text-sm">HTML5</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Proyecto 2: Radio Streaming Platform -->
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-8 text-white border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-400/50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Radio Streaming Platform</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Plataforma avanzada de streaming de radio con m&uacute;ltiples canales, 
              desarrollada con WordPress y tecnolog&iacute;as web modernas, proporcionando 
              una experiencia de usuario excepcional con alta calidad de audio y 
              funcionalidades interactivas.
            </p>
            
